content: @T-libs agenda is once again empty, but that doesn't mean there's nothing to do: lots of PRs are open and waiting for review. so let's spend some time on that. also, I'd really like to work towards some kind of 'roadmap', not with deadlines or a planning or anything like that, but a bit of an overview of what kind of work we think should be done in the libraries. then afterwards we can see if we can get some people enthusiastic about working on those things (not all at the same time ^^)
@T-libs-api meeting in half an hour :tada: agenda: https://hackmd.io/JTC6EA4TTYCxIryhEuJ8tg
